description: Get rate axis chart list. Please apply signature first if both want to use valid chart.

parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is endpoint agent operation is successful

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API system, using to identify your permission to the api. Valid for maximum one month.

parameters.name: time_id
parameters.description: Request unique identifier for a time. Request pairs for time of API.

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated by partner_id and API. Signature method: md5(partner_id+time_id+access_token). For example, the md5 signature generation url: https://www.md5online.org/

parameters.name: page_size
parameters.description: The size of the page. Max=10

parameters.name: center
parameters.description: Specifies the starting point of data to return in the center call. Default is 0 - if data is more than the provided value, only data prior to start will be returned.

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking

response_fields.name: line_chart
response_fields.description: if have count rate data, this value need to in line return center
